Works:

<input type="datetime-local" value="2000-01-01T00:00:00" />
PHP for value (windows safe):

strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S', strtotime($my_datetime_input))






/* show the text field as asterisks in normal mode */
input[name="password"] {
  -webkit-text-security: disc;
}

/* if show password is checked, show the actual text */
input[name="show-password"]:checked ~ input[name="password"] {
  -webkit-text-security: none;
}